title: Now That's Music - Sept..2016 (3-CD Fall Deluxe)  320ak
description:
Now Thats Music - Sept.2016 (3-CD Fall Deluxe) 320ak

This one took me awhile and it is the largest one yet. Thats because there was sooo much new music being released now. And there is such a good selection as well I was getting distracted by album after album and that just made the process of creating this compilation far more difficult and time consuming than normal.

But Fall previews and new releases are anything but normal. Enough of my talk lets get to the ...
